<div class="news__content">
<p class="news__date">admin, 2018-03-10 00:06:58</p>
<h2 class="news__head">Angrathar: Summary!</h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Hi Angrathar community!</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">At the moment of writing this news, <strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">Angrathar</span></strong> is <strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">42 days</span></strong> old and has already reached more than <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>5000 players online&nbsp;</strong></span>simultaneously!&nbsp;So, the time has come for a first summary. This news is pretty long, so if you want to read everyting we would like to share with you, just click <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>"Read More"</strong></span> in the bottom left corner of this news.</p>
</div>
<div class="news__foot">
<a href="/news/32/show">READ MORE <i class="fa fa-fw fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
</div>
</li>
<li class="col-lg-6 news">
<div class="news__image">
<img src="https://sunwell.pl/img/eoe_release.png" alt="Angrathar: The Eye of Eternity!" < div>
<div class="news__content">
<p class="news__date">admin, 2018-02-24 16:53:55</p>
<h2 class="news__head">Angrathar: The Eye of Eternity!</h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Soon it'll be a month since our international realm, <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>Angrathar</strong></span>, has been released. The players need to prepare before the last and the most difficult raid of this PvE content!</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">3</span><span style="color: #ff6600;">rd March, 20:00 GMT+1</span></strong>, marks the opening of <strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">The Eye of Eternity!</span></strong>&nbsp;You will face <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>Malygos</strong></span>, the Spell-Weaver, the Blue Aspect of Magic, leader of the Blue Dragonflight and one of the oldest inhabitants of Azeroth! 10-Man and 25-Man versions of this raid are going to be launched in<strong><span style="color: #ff6600;"> Heroic Mode</span></strong> (greatly increased difficulty)!</p>
</div>
<div class="news__foot">
<a href="/news/31/show">READ MORE <i class="fa fa-fw fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
</div>
</li>
<li class="col-lg-6 news">
<div class="news__image">
<img src="https://sunwell.pl/upload/infoiccimage2.png" alt="Angrathar: Deadly Gladiator, Naxxramas and The Obsidian Sanctum - soon!" < div>
<div class="news__content">
<p class="news__date">admin, 2018-01-29 18:23:16</p>
<h2 class="news__head">Angrathar: Deadly Gladiator, Naxxramas and The Obsidian Sanctum - soon!</h2>
<div data-block="true" data-editor="8kh9d" data-offset-key="197k8-0-0">
<div data-offset-key="197k8-0-0">
<p style="text-align: justify;">Angrathar has just started, but you need to start playing <strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">TODAY</span></strong>!</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>First PvE and PvP seasons</strong></span> begin on <strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">17th February!</span></strong> During the last Sunday, Angrathar had <strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">over 4000 players online.</span></strong> Join us and begin your epic journey on our new, international Wrath of the Lich King realm!</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">We remind you that on our second realm, Feronis, Fall of the Lich King and Wrathful Gladiator season will begin on <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>21st February!</strong></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;" data-block="true" data-editor="8kh9d" data-offset-key="dpjb3-0-0">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
<div class="news__foot">
<a href="/news/30/show">READ MORE <i class="fa fa-fw fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
